snippet.title: Exploring Genshin Impact! - More Shadows Amidst Snowstorms Event!
snippet.description:
Thank you all so much for over 31,500 subscribers! Join us today as we explore the world of Genshin Impact!
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
♞ DISCORD ♞
Feel free to join our Discord to find out when I am going to stream! :D https://discord.com/invite/VzHn223
You can also join along in our everyday chat rooms where you can share random thoughts, ask questions and even share your own Youtube videos or artwork! :D 

🎮 Twitch 🎮
Follow me on Twitch for more livestreams! I don't stream Genshin on Twitch, however I play many other games and sometimes just chat to you lot, come and say hi! - https://www.twitch.tv/abraxos_

☃ DONATIONS ☃
Donating to the stream is completely optional, I stream purely for fun and to entertain, however if you want to donate then you can via this link https://streamlabs.com/abraxos or alternitively consider becoming a member (Just click the join button below the stream)! 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
↓ Please read the terms below before donating! ↓
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Be responsible when donating, if you are using someone else's money, make sure you have their permission!

INTRO SONG:
TheFatRat - Electrified
https://youtu.be/p-LOXXGGeAc
